{
  "__inputs": [
    {
      "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
      "label": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Prometheus datasource for PeeringDB Plus metrics",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "prometheus",
      "pluginName": "Prometheus"
    }
  ],
  "__requires": [
    {
      "type": "grafana",
      "id": "grafana",
      "name": "Grafana",
      "version": "10.0.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "datasource",
      "id": "prometheus",
      "name": "Prometheus",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "gauge",
      "name": "Gauge",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "graph",
      "name": "Graph",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "stat",
      "name": "Stat",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "text",
      "name": "Text",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "timeseries",
      "name": "Time series",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "table",
      "name": "Table",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "barchart",
      "name": "Bar chart",
      "version": ""
    }
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": {
          "type": "grafana",
          "uid": "-- Grafana --"
        },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "description": "Comprehensive monitoring dashboard for PeeringDB Plus: sync health, HTTP traffic, per-type sync detail, Go runtime, and business metrics.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "panels": [
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "title": "Sync Health",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "description": "**Sync Health** monitors PeeringDB data freshness and sync pipeline reliability.\n\n- **Data Freshness**: Seconds since last successful sync. Green (<1h) = healthy, Yellow (<2h) = stale, Red (>2h) = critical.\n- **Sync Duration**: How long each sync cycle takes. Increasing trends may indicate PeeringDB API slowdowns.\n- **Success/Failure Rate**: Track sync reliability. Any failures should be investigated via per-type error panels below.\n- **Fallback Events**: Incremental-to-full sync fallbacks per type. Frequent fallbacks may indicate data integrity issues.\n\n**Troubleshooting**: If freshness is red, check sync failure rate and per-type errors. If duration is increasing, check PeeringDB API status.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "id": 101,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Sync Health** monitors PeeringDB data freshness and sync pipeline reliability.\n\n- **Data Freshness**: Seconds since last successful sync. Green (<1h) = healthy, Yellow (<2h) = stale, Red (>2h) = critical.\n- **Sync Duration**: How long each sync cycle takes. Increasing trends may indicate PeeringDB API slowdowns.\n- **Success/Failure Rate**: Track sync reliability. Any failures should be investigated via per-type error panels below.\n- **Fallback Events**: Incremental-to-full sync fallbacks per type. Frequent fallbacks may indicate data integrity issues.\n\n**Troubleshooting**: If freshness is red, check sync failure rate and per-type errors. If duration is increasing, check PeeringDB API status."
      },
      "title": "About Sync Health",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 3600 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 7200 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "s",
          "max": 14400,
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
      "id": 102,
      "options": {
        "minVizHeight": 75,
        "minVizWidth": 75,
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "showThresholdLabels": true,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "pdbplus_sync_freshness_seconds",
          "legendFormat": "Data Freshness",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Data Freshness",
      "type": "gauge"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisLabel": "",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 5 },
      "id": 103,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(pdbplus_sync_duration_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "p95",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, rate(pdbplus_sync_duration_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Sync Duration",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 50,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" }
          },
          "unit": "ops"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "failed" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "success" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 5 },
      "id": 104,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["sum"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "rate(pdbplus_sync_operations_total{status=\"success\"}[$__rate_interval])",
          "legendFormat": "success",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "rate(pdbplus_sync_operations_total{status=\"failed\"}[$__rate_interval])",
          "legendFormat": "failed",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Sync Success / Failure Rate",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 30,
            "lineWidth": 1
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 5 },
      "id": 105,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["sum"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "rate(pdbplus_sync_type_fallback_total[$__rate_interval])",
          "legendFormat": "{{type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Fallback Events by Type",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 11 },
      "id": 200,
      "title": "HTTP RED Metrics",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "id": 201,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**HTTP RED Metrics** (Rate, Errors, Duration) monitor API traffic health.\n\n- **Request Rate**: Requests per second by HTTP route. Spikes may indicate scraping or traffic surges.\n- **Error Rate**: 4xx (client errors) and 5xx (server errors). Sustained 5xx errors indicate application issues.\n- **Latency Percentiles**: p50 (typical), p95 (slow), p99 (worst case). High p99 with normal p50 suggests tail latency issues.\n- **Active Requests**: Currently in-flight HTTP requests. Sustained high values may indicate connection pooling issues.\n\n**Troubleshooting**: High error rates with normal latency = bad requests. High latency with normal error rate = backend slowdown (check sync or DB)."
      },
      "title": "About HTTP RED Metrics",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" }
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "id": 202,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum by (http_route) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{http_route}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Request Rate by Route",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" }
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": "5xx" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": "4xx" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 16 },
      "id": 203,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "sum"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{http_response_status_code=~\"4..\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "4xx",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{http_response_status_code=~\"5..\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "5xx",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Error Rate (4xx / 5xx)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 1
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 16 },
      "id": 204,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ],
      "title": "HTTP Latency Percentiles",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineWidth": 1
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 16 },
      "id": 205,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "http_server_active_requests",
          "legendFormat": "Active Requests",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Active HTTP Requests",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 22 },
      "id": 300,
      "title": "Per-Type Sync Detail",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 23 },
      "id": 301,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Per-Type Sync Detail** breaks down sync performance by PeeringDB object type (org, net, ix, fac, etc.).\n\n- **Duration by Type**: How long each type takes to sync. Large types (net, poc) naturally take longer.\n- **Object Counts**: Number of objects upserted per type per sync cycle. Sudden drops may indicate API issues.\n- **Delete Counts**: Objects removed per type. High delete counts with no corresponding PeeringDB changes may indicate sync bugs.\n- **Fetch/Upsert Errors**: API fetch failures and database write errors by type. Non-zero values need investigation.\n\n**Troubleshooting**: If one type consistently fails, check PeeringDB API for that endpoint. If upsert errors spike, check SQLite disk space and LiteFS health."
      },
      "title": "About Per-Type Sync Detail",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 1
          },
          "unit": "s"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 27 },
      "id": 302,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, type) (rate(pdbplus_sync_type_duration_seconds_bucket[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Sync Duration by Type (p95)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 50,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" }
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 27 },
      "id": 303,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["sum"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "rate(pdbplus_sync_type_objects_total[$__rate_interval])",
          "legendFormat": "{{type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Object Counts by Type",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 50,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "normal" }
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 27 },
      "id": 304,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["sum"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "rate(pdbplus_sync_type_deleted_total[$__rate_interval])",
          "legendFormat": "{{type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Delete Counts by Type",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "lineWidth": 1
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 27 },
      "id": 305,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["sum"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
