    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 33 },
      "id": 400,
      "title": "Go Runtime",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 34 },
      "id": 401,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Go Runtime** metrics from the OTel runtime instrumentation library.\n\n- **Goroutines**: Active goroutine count. Steady growth without plateau indicates goroutine leaks.\n- **Heap Memory**: Current heap allocation. Should be bounded by GOMEMLIMIT (set via automemlimit from cgroup).\n- **Allocation Rate**: Bytes allocated per second. High allocation rate increases GC pressure.\n- **GC Goal**: The Go runtime's target heap size for the next GC cycle. Compares with actual heap usage.\n\n**Troubleshooting**: If goroutines grow unbounded, check for leaked sync workers or HTTP handlers. If heap approaches GOMEMLIMIT, consider increasing VM memory."
      },
      "title": "About Go Runtime",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "lineWidth": 1
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 38 },
      "id": 402,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "calcs": ["mean", "max"], "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "expr": "process_runtime_go_goroutines",
          "legendFormat": "Goroutines",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Goroutines",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
